---
import DetailLayout from '../layouts/DetailLayout.astro';
---
<DetailLayout title="Momento">

  <section class="site-section" id="section-project-info">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row mb-5 align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-6 pr-lg-5 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
          <div class="device-wrapper">
            <div class="device" data-device="Pixel" data-orientation="portrait" data-color="black">
              <div class="screen">
                <img src="/images/momento_main.gif" class="sketch-main-img">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <h2><strong>Momento</strong></h2>
          </div>
          <p><span class="date"><span class="icon-calendar"></span> November 2020 - June 2022 </span></p>
          <p class="lead">배너 • 네이티브 • 동영상 광고 송출이 가능한 SDK</p>
          <p class="mb-5">배너 • 네이티브 • 동영상 광고 기능 설계와 개발
            <br>매체별 수익 고도화를 위한 품질 관리와 연동 이슈 대응
            <br>Kotlin • Java 등을 활용한 개발
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="site-section bg-light" id="section-works">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 mb-5">
          <div class="section-heading text-center"><h2>My <strong>Works</strong></h2></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal1">
            <h3>동영상 광고</h3>
            <span class="school">#vast #xml_parse #media_player_2</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal3">
            <h3>네이티브 광고</h3>
            <span class="school">#custom_view #bind_view</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal2">
            <h3>배너 광고</h3>
            <span class="school">#web_view #web_view_client</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal4">
            <h3>매체별 품질 관리와 연동 이슈 대응</h3>
            <span class="school">#firebase #crashlytics #big_query</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modal 1 -->
  <div class="portfolio-modal modal fade" id="portfolioModal1" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog"><div class="modal-content">
      <div class="close-modal" data-dismiss="modal"><div class="lr"><div class="rl"></div></div></div>
      <div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto"><div class="modal-body">
        <h3>동영상 광고</h3><br>
        <div id="carouselForModal1" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/video/1.jpeg"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/video/2.jpeg"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/video/3.jpeg"></div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselForModal1" role="button" data-slide="prev"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></div></a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselForModal1" role="button" data-slide="next"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></div></a>
        </div><br>
        <div class="section-heading text-center"><h3>주요 기능과 구현 특징</h3><br></div>
        <div class="detail-desc">
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbspVAST 3.0 표준 XML 파싱과 광고 데이터 관리</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp동영상 광고 데이터 서버 요청</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp동영상 광고 송출</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp매체에서 사용할 동영상 광고의 메소드와 콜백 정의</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp동영상 광고 송출 시 VAST 3.0 표준에 맞는 트래킹</h4></div>
        </div>
      </div></div></div></div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Modal 2 -->
  <div class="portfolio-modal modal fade" id="portfolioModal2" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog"><div class="modal-content">
      <div class="close-modal" data-dismiss="modal"><div class="lr"><div class="rl"></div></div></div>
      <div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto"><div class="modal-body">
        <h3>배너 광고</h3><br>
        <div id="carouselForModal2" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/banner/1.jpeg"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/banner/2.jpeg"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/banner/3.jpeg"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/banner/4.jpeg"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/banner/5.jpeg"></div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselForModal2" role="button" data-slide="prev"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></div></a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselForModal2" role="button" data-slide="next"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></div></a>
        </div><br>
        <div class="section-heading text-center"><h3>주요 기능과 구현 내용</h3><br></div>
        <div class="detail-desc">
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp배너 광고 데이터 서버 요청</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp배너 광고 송출</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp매체에서 사용할 배너 광고의 메소드와 콜백 정의</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp배너 광고 송출 시 상황에 따른 트래킹</h4></div>
        </div>
      </div></div></div></div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Modal 3 -->
  <div class="portfolio-modal modal fade" id="portfolioModal3" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog"><div class="modal-content">
      <div class="close-modal" data-dismiss="modal"><div class="lr"><div class="rl"></div></div></div>
      <div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto"><div class="modal-body">
        <h3>네이티브 광고</h3><br>
        <div id="carouselForModal3" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/native/1.jpeg"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/native/2.jpeg"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/native/3.jpeg"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/native/4.jpeg"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="/images/screenshots/momento/native/5.jpeg"></div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselForModal3" role="button" data-slide="prev"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></div></a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselForModal3" role="button" data-slide="next"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></div></a>
        </div><br>
        <div class="section-heading text-center"><h3>주요 기능과 구현 내용</h3><br></div>
        <div class="detail-desc">
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp네이티브 광고 데이터 서버 요청</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp네이티브 광고 송출</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp매체에서 사용할 네이티브 광고의 메소드와 콜백 정의</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp네이티브 광고 송출 시 상황에 따른 트래킹</h4></div>
        </div>
      </div></div></div></div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Modal 4 -->
  <div class="portfolio-modal modal fade" id="portfolioModal4" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog"><div class="modal-content">
      <div class="close-modal" data-dismiss="modal"><div class="lr"><div class="rl"></div></div></div>
      <div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto"><div class="modal-body">
        <h3>매체별 품질 관리와 연동 이슈 대응</h3><br>
        <div id="carouselForModal4" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active"><img class="parse-item" src="/images/screenshots/momento/firebase/1.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="parse-item" src="/images/screenshots/momento/firebase/2.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="parse-item" src="/images/screenshots/momento/firebase/3.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="parse-item" src="/images/screenshots/momento/firebase/4.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="parse-item" src="/images/screenshots/momento/firebase/5.png"></div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselForModal4" role="button" data-slide="prev"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></div></a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselForModal4" role="button" data-slide="next"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></div></a>
        </div><br>
        <div class="section-heading text-center"><h3>주요 기능과 구현 내용</h3><br></div>
        <div class="detail-desc">
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbspFirebase Crashlytics를 통한 매체별 크래시 관리와 대응</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbspGoogle Cloud BigQuery를 통한 매체별 광고 수치 분석과 대응</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp매체별 광고 연동에 대한 F/U</h4></div>
        </div>
      </div></div></div></div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

</DetailLayout>
